(297, 1, '2016-06-14 10:15:00', '2016-06-14 16:15:00', '<div class="office-text">\r\n<h3>Our Firm</h3>\r\nOur Colorado Springs, Colorado, law firm, founded in 1977, is a well-known and respected presence throughout central and southern Colorado.\r\nWe offer a free informative consultation by calling 719.520.0003to help each client assess legal options and risks before deciding on a course of action.\r\n\r\n<em>Three Proven, Approachable and Helpful Lawyers</em>\r\n\r\nYou may recognize the names of attorneys Kenton D. Kinnaird, Sean Cloyes and Jason A. Kinnaird from radio appearances and coverage in other local media. If so, you may also have the accurate impression that our attorneys are approachable, articulate people with a genuine drive to inform and help people with their legal problems.\r\n\r\n<em>A Skilled Legal Support Staff Adds Strength and Depth</em>\r\n\r\nOur team of paralegals and support personnel work extremely hard to support and advance your objectives. When your legal matter requires thorough research, document processing and other efforts essential to achieving your goals, this work is in good hands. As a group, we are responsive and deeply committed to client satisfaction.\r\n\r\nAt Kinnaird Cloyes &amp; Kinnaird, P.C., we have a long tradition of providing personal attention and practical solutions. Whether you are facing an unfortunate <a href="http://kcklaw.com/about.php">bankruptcy</a>, painful <a href="http://kcklaw.com/about.php">divorce</a> or challenges associated with <a href="http://kcklaw.com/about.php">personal injury</a>\r\nWe know how to deal with your tough legal problems, and encourage you to contact us for a free initial consultation.\r\n\r\nCall us today at 719.520.0003 | Or send us a message from our <a href="http://kcklaw.com/contact.php">contact page</a>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="office-img">\r\n<p class="img-small small"><img class="size-full wp-image-129 alignright" src="http://localhost:99/kcklaw/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/building.png" alt="Our building at 415 W. Bijou St." width="246" height="380" /></p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="staff-img">\r\n\r\n<a class="anchor" name="profiles"></a>\r\n<div class="at-text">\r\n<h3>Our Attorneys</h3>\r\nWe focus on personal injury, divorce, and bankruptcy to help the well-being of citizens from Woodland Park and Palmer Lake to Pueblo, Colorado, and throughout the region. We are maintaining and building upon a strong tradition of representing people with strength, compassion and conscience.\r\n\r\nWe are a close-knit, collaborative group of professionals who combine legal education with a wealth of experience. Our entire firm is committed to providing personal, caring service and delivering the effort that gets results for you.\r\n\r\nYou can view profiles with more information on our attorneys'' backgrounds and accomplishments below.\r\n\r\n<a href="http://207.210.201.253/~kcklaw/about-us/attorneys/kenton-d-kinnaird/">Kenton D. Kinnaird</a> | <a href="http://207.210.201.253/~kcklaw/about-us/attorneys/sean-cloyes/">Sean Cloyes</a> | <a href="http://207.210.201.253/~kcklaw/about-us/attorneys/jason-e-kinnaird/">Jason A. Kinnaird</a>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'About Us', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '9-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-06-14 10:15:00', '2016-06-14 16:15:00', '', 9, 'http://207.210.201.253/~kcklaw/9-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
